label: eventType
comment: A code representing the type of EPCIS event. ObjectEvent, AggregationEvent, TransactionEvent, TransformationEvent, ObjectEvent.

rangeIncludes.comment: A code describing the traceability event type - drawn from GS1 EPCIS 2.0

domainIncludes.comment: The TraceabilityEvent class represents a specific EPCIS event in the traceability chain of a product, including details about the event type and reference.
